    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Key Pieces in the Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Puma Golf x PTC AW24 Collection features several standout pieces that are sure to become staples in your golf wardrobe. Each piece embodies the relaxed yet high-performance ethos of the collection, making them perfect for both casual rounds and competitive play.</p><h3><strong>1. Palm Glitch Polo (Sparkling Green/Fresh Mint)</strong></h3><p>This polo is one of the most eye-catching pieces in the collection. With its glitch-inspired palm tree print and vibrant colourway, the Palm Glitch Polo is perfect for golfers who want to make a statement. Made from high-quality performance fabrics, it ensures comfort and flexibility throughout your game, while its modern aesthetic keeps you looking stylish.</p><h3><strong>2. Resort Polo (Deep Navy/Sparkling Green)</strong></h3><p>The Resort Polo is the ideal blend of performance and laid-back style. With a performance fit that ensures a full range of motion, and a chic chain-link print, this polo is perfect for those who want to maintain comfort without compromising on style. Whether you're playing a competitive round or enjoying a leisurely day on the course, the Resort Polo has you covered.</p><h3><strong>3. Jacquard Polo (Sparkling Green)</strong></h3><p>For those who appreciate subtle luxury, the Jacquard Polo in Sparkling Green is a must-have. This polo is made from Puma's ultra-soft CLOUDSPUN fabric, which delivers a soft, comfortable feel against the skin while still offering high-performance moisture-wicking capabilities. The tonal jacquard palm pattern adds a touch of sophistication, making this polo perfect for golfers who want a refined, understated look.</p><h3><strong>4. Half Zip Palm Fleece (Deep Navy/Sparkling Green)</strong></h3><p>When the weather cools down, the Half Zip Palm Fleece is the perfect layering piece. This fleece not only keeps you warm but also stays true to the collection's tropical aesthetic with its bold palm tree accents. Ideal for early morning rounds or breezy afternoons, this fleece offers both style and functionality, ensuring you stay comfortable no matter the conditions.</p>"
