        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A key element of the Puma Golf x PTC AW24 Collection is the prominent use of the Palm Tree Crew logo - a palm tree merged into the Puma 'P' that symbolises the laid-back luxury that Kygo's brand represents. This logo can be found across the entire collection, subtly reinforcing the idea that golf fashion can be fun, relaxed, and luxurious all at once.</p><p>The branding in this collection emphasises the idea that you don't have to choose between performance and style. Whether you're on the green or off, the Puma Golf x Palm Tree Crew AW24 Collection allows you to express your personality and channel your inner holiday mode.</p><h2><strong>Why The Puma Golf x Palm Tree Crew AW24 Collection is Perfect for You</strong></h2><p>If you're someone who values both performance and aesthetics in your golf wardrobe, the Puma Golf x PTC AW24 Collection is for you. This collection not only delivers on the technical aspects required for a great round of golf - such as breathability, comfort, and flexibility - but also allows you to showcase your personality and love for a more relaxed, tropical-inspired lifestyle.</p><h2><strong>A Fashion-Forward Approach to Golf Apparel</strong></h2><p>Gone are the days when golf fashion had to be stiff and boring. The Puma Golf x PTC AW24 Collection brings a breath of fresh air to the golf course, with its vibrant colours, bold patterns, and luxurious fabrics. Whether you're a seasoned pro or a casual player, this collection offers something for everyone, allowing you to stand out in style while staying comfortable and performing your best.</p><h2><strong>Perfect for On and Off the Course</strong></h2><p>One of the best features of this collection is its versatility. While designed for the golf course, many of these pieces can easily transition into your everyday wardrobe. Whether you're heading to a beachside bar or a casual dinner after a round of golf, the Puma Golf x PTC AW24 Collection ensures you'll look effortlessly stylish no matter the setting.</p><h2><strong>Get Ready to Turn Heads</strong></h2><p>With its combination of performance-driven design and beach-inspired style, the Puma Golf x Palm Tree Crew AW24 Collection is set to turn heads. Whether you're drawn to the bold prints of the Palm Glitch Polo or the understated elegance of the Jacquard Polo, this collection has something for every golfer who wants to bring a little bit of the tropics to their game.</p>"
